{"tid":1232794,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解讀真理越辯越明 ?","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T15:33:41.000Z","uid":70760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d46cd670bfdaaf0249374850d0bfc00857a33f49","tid":1232794,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"是否正確 仲有係指邊種真理 越明係一個咩狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712bebe05a4be7decb04fc35bd8e40411a7729a5","tid":1232794,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294feed026592639b20a190948222d826b9c7e01","tid":1232794,"uid":249015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"施主 點解咁問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115d408ee400be66e5794c95096ac93ed41ed0dc","tid":1232794,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"要知真理係唔係越辯越明，噉首先要知真理係咩。<br />\n<br />\n首先真理必定恆真？<br />\n<br />\n同意嘅話會去咗，恆真句到底可唔可以有意義噉描述經驗世界呢？<br />\n<br />\n反對嘅話會去咗，若果真理只係適然，噉仲係唔係我地想指嘅真理呢。<br />\n<br />\n若果真理係指描述經驗世界嘅一句必然真嘅描述，噉真理存唔存在？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔存在，噉同講獨角獸越跑越快無分別。<br />\n<br />\n如果存在，佢係唔係越辯越明就要試下辯佢啦。"},{"pid":"1d165c5be66c857dc725a3f7b2b22bdbcbfd78a7","tid":1232794,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"真理越辯越明語境上想表達嘅應該係<br />\n<br />\n1. 某人經過理性且正確的推論後，理應能對某事作出一個真值為真的描述<br />\n2. 句1為真"},{"pid":"27eb87d3f7c0d3495026a325d5d64782c37c5d11","tid":1232794,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"辯論會將錯誤嘅野剔除"}]}